<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Golden Crumb | Home-Baked Millet Goods</title>
    <style>
        /* Rustic, warm bakery color palette */
        :root {
            --primary-bg: #FAF6F0; /* Cream */
            --text-dark: #3E2723; /* Dark brown */
            --accent-gold: #D4A373; /* Golden baked brown */
            --whatsapp-green: #25D366;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--primary-bg);
            color: var(--text-dark);
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 3rem 1rem;
            background-color: var(--accent-gold);
            color: white;
        }

        header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }

        header p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-top: 10px;
            font-style: italic;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 2rem 1rem;
        }

        /* --- NEW: Promise Section Styles --- */
        .promise-section {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: 1px solid #EAE0D5;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.02);
        }

        .promise-section h2 {
            color: var(--text-dark);
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
        }

        .promise-intro {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto 40px auto;
            color: #555;
            line-height: 1.6;
            font-size: 1.05rem;
        }

        .promise-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
            gap: 25px;
        }

        .promise-card {
            background-color: var(--primary-bg);
            padding: 25px 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: 1px solid #EAE0D5;
            transition: transform 0.2s ease;
        }

        .promise-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
        }

        .promise-icon {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .promise-card h3 {
            color: var(--accent-gold);
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }

        .promise-card p {
            color: #666;
            line-height: 1.5;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            margin: 0;
        }
        /* --- END: Promise Section Styles --- */

        .products-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }

        .product-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            text-align: center;
            border: 1px solid #EAE0D5;
        }

        .product-card h3 {
            color: var(--accent-gold);
            margin-top: 0;
        }

        .price {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: var(--text-dark);
            margin: 10px 0;
        }

        .whatsapp-btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: var(--whatsapp-green);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-top: 15px;
            transition: transform 0.2s;
        }

        .whatsapp-btn:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #777;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <h1>Golden Crumb</h1>
        <p>Wholesome, home-baked millet goodness from our kitchen to yours.</p>
    </header>

    <div class="container">
        
        <!-- NEW: Our Promise Section -->
        <section class="promise-section">
            <h2>Our Promise: Real Ingredients, No Shortcuts</h2>
            <p class="promise-intro">
                We trade the commercial bakery playbook for the ingredients our grandmothers trusted. 
                No chemistry-lab additives—just honest, earth-grown goodness baked fresh in our Chennai kitchen.
            </p>
            
            <div class="promise-grid">
                <div class="promise-card">
                    <div class="promise-icon">🌾</div>
                    <h3>100% Traditional Millets</h3>
                    <p>We proudly bake with nutrient-dense indigenous grains like Ragi, Thinai, and Bajra, leaving empty calories and refined maida behind.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="promise-card">
                    <div class="promise-icon">🚫</div>
                    <h3>Zero Preservatives</h3>
                    <p>Real food has a shelf life. We never use artificial stabilizers or chemicals, ensuring every bite is fresh, safe, and completely natural.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="promise-card">
                    <div class="promise-icon">🍯</div>
                    <h3>Naturally Sweetened</h3>
                    <p>We sweeten our bakes exclusively with unrefined alternatives like jaggery and raw cane, giving you the indulgence you crave without the sugar crash.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <h2 style="text-align: center;">Our Freshly Baked Menu</h2>
        
        <div class="products-grid">
            
            <!-- Product 1 -->
            <div class="product-card">
                <h3>Ragi Chocolate Cookies</h3>
                <p>Rich, fudgy cookies made with organic finger millet and dark chocolate chunks. 100% guilt-free.</p>
                <div class="price">₹250 / Box of 6</div>
                <a href="https://wa.me/917305590333?text=Hi%20Golden%20Crumb!%20I%20would%20like%20to%20order%20the%20Ragi%20Chocolate%20Cookies." class="whatsapp-btn" target="_blank">Order via WhatsApp</a>
            </div>

            <!-- Product 2 -->
            <div class="product-card">
                <h3>Pearl Millet Banana Bread</h3>
                <p>Moist and naturally sweet banana loaf baked with wholesome Bajra. Perfect for morning tea.</p>
                <div class="price">₹350 / Loaf</div>
                <a href="https://wa.me/917305590333?text=Hi%20Golden%20Crumb!%20I%20would%20like%20to%20order%20the%20Pearl%20Millet%20Banana%20Bread." class="whatsapp-btn" target="_blank">Order via WhatsApp</a>
            </div>

            <!-- Product 3 -->
            <div class="product-card">
                <h3>Foxtail Millet Brownies</h3>
                <p>Dense, gooey brownies packed with the nutritional power of Thinai. Refined sugar-free.</p>
                <div class="price">₹400 / Box of 4</div>
                <a href="https://wa.me/917305590333?text=Hi%20Golden%20Crumb!%20I%20would%20like%20to%20order%20the%20Foxtail%20Millet%20Brownies." class="whatsapp-btn" target="_blank">Order via WhatsApp</a>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2026 Golden Crumb. Proudly baked in Chennai.</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>